OL,3,CWoman faces E34,000 medical bill after
OL,4,Cinsurance was invalidated because of
OL,5,CHRT
OL,7,FReport by ITV News Correspondent
OL,8,FStacey Foster. Words by ITV News
OL,9,FProducer Catherine Dinneny.
OL,11,FA woman who needed urgent hospital
OL,12,Ftreatment while on holiday has been
OL,13,Frefused a pay out by her insurers
OL,14,Fbecause she failed to declare her
OL,15,Fmenopause medication.
OL,17,FElle Dennis had a seizure while on
OL,18,Fholiday in Majorca last year and
OL,19,Fneeded to be put into an induced coma,
OL,20,Fresulting in hospital stay costing
OL,21,FE34,000 (#28,000).
