OL,7,FBut her claim has been denied by her
OL,8,Finsurer because she didn't mention
OL,9,Fthat she had been prescribed Hormone
OL,10,FReplacement Therapy when she renewed
OL,11,Fher policy - even though the
OL,12,Fmedication was unrelated to her fit.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News, she said: "I
OL,15,Ffeel really depressed and angry and
OL,16,Fworried. I don't know how I'm going to
OL,17,Fever pay the bill."
