OL,7,FShe only started taking the medication
OL,8,Fat the end of April last year, just
OL,9,Fweeks before the couple went away with
OL,10,Ftheir children.
OL,12,FShe said: "I'd only just got the
OL,13,Ftablets, literally just before we went
OL,14,Fon holiday. I hadn't really taken
OL,15,Fthem."
OL,17,FIt was the first day of their holiday
OL,18,Fwhen Elle was rushed to hospital after
OL,19,Fhaving a seizure. She was put in an
OL,20,Finduced coma and had to stay in a
OL,21,Fprivate clinic for seven days.
