OL,7,FTests carried out while she was in
OL,8,Fhospital in Palma revealed she has a
OL,9,Fgrade three brain tumour.
OL,11,F"I actually asked that question (if it
OL,12,Fwas connected to HRT) and they said
OL,13,Fit's nothing to do with it at all,"
OL,14,FElle said.
OL,16,FHer husband Neal added: "The doctors
OL,17,Fwere saying don't worry because you
OL,18,Fwill be covered under your insurance,
OL,19,Fthere's no way that you won't be
OL,20,Fcovered.
