OL,7,F"We'd taken out medical insurance,
OL,8,Fwe'd taken our European health card.
OL,9,FShe was in a critical condition so the
OL,10,Fconcern was with trying to find out
OL,11,Fwhat exactly was going on."
OL,13,FNeal contacted Inter Parter
OL,14,FAssistance, part of the AXA group,
OL,15,Fwhile Elle was still in hospital.
OL,17,FWhen they received her medical records
OL,18,Fand saw that she was taking HRT, they
OL,19,Ftold Neal that she wasn't covered.
