OL,5,CHRT
OL,7,FHe said: "We didn't believe HRT was a
OL,8,Fpre-existing condition that had to be
OL,9,Fdeclared. Had we declared HRT, they
OL,10,Fwould have insured us as we understand
OL,11,Fit at no extra cost, just on a
OL,12,Fdifferent type of insurance policy, so
OL,13,Fit's a bit of a loop hole that they're
OL,14,Ftrying to use to get out of paying
OL,15,Fthis large bill."
OL,17,FElle added: "Every woman goes through
OL,18,Fthe menopause. It's not a real medical
OL,19,Fcondition, it's just part of life, so
OL,20,Fit didn't even cross my mind (to
OL,21,Fdeclare it)."
