OL,7,FElle and her husband Neal, who live in
OL,8,FRugeley in Staffordshire, are now
OL,9,Fbeing chased by debt collectors for
OL,10,Fthe money - all while Elle is
OL,11,Fundergoing gruelling cancer treatment
OL,12,Fback in the UK and unable to work.
OL,14,FThe couple have even complained to the
OL,15,FOmbudsman, who has ruled in favour of
OL,16,Fthe insurance company.
