OL,7,FIn a letter sent to them, seen by ITV
OL,8,FNews, the Ombudsman wrote: "I've taken
OL,9,Fon board the point that Mr and Mrs D
OL,10,Fmay have ended up with a similarly
OL,11,Fbranded travel insurance policy (...)
OL,12,Fhowever, I don't think that matters."
OL,14,FHe added that it was reasonable to
OL,15,Fexpect IPA to refund the premium paid
OL,16,Ffor the policy - #36.45.
OL,18,FElle is now warning other women who
OL,19,Fare going through the menopause to
OL,20,Fcheck that they are covered when
OL,21,Ftravelling abroad.
