OL,7,FShe said: "Declare everything, it's
OL,8,Fjust not worth it."
OL,10,FWhat advice is available to insurance
OL,11,Fcustomers?
OL,13,FRob Lilley-Jones, a consumer expert at
OL,14,FWhich?, said this case was unfair but
OL,15,Fadvised everyone to thoroughly check
OL,16,Ftheir policies because companies are
OL,17,Fincreasingly reluctant to pay out
OL,18,Fclaims.
