OL,7,F"Travellers aren't declaring medical
OL,8,Fconditions because, unfortunately,
OL,9,Fpremiums are going up and they're
OL,10,Fworried that if they declare those
OL,11,Fillnesses, the premiums will get
OL,12,Fhigher, but we do know that insurers
OL,13,Fwill go through the small print with a
OL,14,Ffine tooth comb."
OL,16,FHe added: "It's really on the insurers
OL,17,Fto do better and to make sure that
OL,18,Fpeople don't end up in the scenario
OL,19,Flike we have in this case."
